Win a FREE trip to Evo Vegas and compete with the Pros: https://playst.cc/road-to-evo-2025
17 champions have conquered the Road to Evo 2024 qualifiers and are now traveling from all over the world to compete in the ultimate fighting game showdown in Las Vegas. From Street Fighter 6 to Tekken 8, witness their journey as they battle for glory on the world’s biggest FGC stage.
Want to play in this year’s Road to Evo and get your own chance to compete on the world stage? Sign up now: https://playst.cc/road-to-evo-2025

Learn more about PlayStation Esports: https://playst.cc/40fH8zZ
